    {
        "url": "/quotes/katha_pollitt_784249",
        "quote": "Abortion opponents say women seek abortions in haste and confusion. Pro-choicers reply: Abortion is the most difficult, agonizing decision a woman ever makes.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Katha Pollitt",
            "url": "/quotes/katha_pollitt_784249"
        },
        "topics": [
