            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/katha_pollitt_784279",
        "quote": "Ariel may look a lot like Barbie, and her adventure may be limited to romance and over with the wedding bells, but unlike, say, Cinderella or Sleeping Beauty, she's active, brave and determined, the heroine of her own life. She even rescues the prince. And that makes her a rare fish, indeed, in the world of preschool culture.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Katha Pollitt",
            "url": "/quotes/katha_pollitt_784279"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Beauty",
                "url": "/topics/beauty"
            },
            {
                "name": "Romance",
                "url": "/topics/romance"
            },
            {
                "name": "Bells",
                "url": "/topics/bells"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/katha_pollitt_784278",
        "quote": "We do not have the idea that all children are valuable parts of society. We only have the idea that our own children are.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Katha Pollitt",
            "url": "/quotes/katha_pollitt_784278"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Children",
                "url": "/topics/children"
            },
            {
                "name": "Society",
                "url": "/topics/society"
            },
            {
                "name": "Idea",
                "url": "/topics/idea"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/katha_pollitt_784256",
        "quote": "I think women have the right to consult their own wishes, needs, and capacities and produce only loved, wanted children they can care for - or even no children at all. I think we would all be better off as a society if we respected women's ability to make these decisions for themselves and concentrated on caring well for the born.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Katha Pollitt",
            "url": "/quotes/katha_pollitt_784256"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Society",
                "url": "/topics/society"
            },
            {
                "name": "I Think",
                "url": "/topics/i_think"
            },
            {
                "name": "Own",
                "url": "/topics/own"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/katha_pollitt_784255",
        "quote": "A potential person is not a person, any more than an acorn is an oak tree. I don't think women should have to give birth just because a sperm met an egg.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Katha Pollitt",
            "url": "/quotes/katha_pollitt_784255"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Egg",
