    {
        "url": "/quotes/katha_pollitt_784275",
        "quote": "If you have been vaccinated for polio, mumps, measles, chicken pox, hepatitis, or rabies, it may be too late for you to stand your ethical ground: You have already benefited from fetal-tissue research. This is, after all, a practice that's been legal since the 1930s.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Katha Pollitt",
            "url": "/quotes/katha_pollitt_784275"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Practice",
