            {
                "name": "Clinics",
                "url": "/topics/clinics"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/katha_pollitt_784272",
        "quote": "Do men drop out of college because they get someone pregnant? Do they quit their job if they get someone pregnant? No. And we do not require men to support women they have made pregnant. Once the baby is born, there can be child support. Before that, though, no.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Katha Pollitt",
            "url": "/quotes/katha_pollitt_784272"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "College",
