    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/katha_pollitt_784269",
        "quote": "My mother had an illegal abortion in 1960, which was the year the birth control pill came out, but I guess a little late for her, but - and I never knew. I found out when my father, after her death, got her FBI file.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Katha Pollitt",
            "url": "/quotes/katha_pollitt_784269"
        },
        "topics": [
