    {
        "url": "/quotes/katha_pollitt_784251",
        "quote": "Most Americans probably have no idea how hostile anti-abortion sidewalk counseling outside clinics can be. There's a reason pro-choicers volunteer to escort patients as they make their way past angry crowds to the clinic door.",
