    {
        "url": "/quotes/katha_pollitt_784274",
        "quote": "We want to make sure that women have a way to use all their gifts in society, to get educated, to be all they can be in the workforce, to really develop as people in all the ways that they can. We want this for men too! And we want this for children. Well this can't happen if this can be sandbagged by an ill-timed and unwanted pregnancy.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Katha Pollitt",
            "url": "/quotes/katha_pollitt_784274"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Society",
