    {
        "url": "/quotes/katha_pollitt_784250",
        "quote": "We need to say that women have sex, have abortions, are at peace with the decision, and move on with their lives. We need to say that is their right, and, moreover, it's good for everyone that they have this right: The whole society benefits when motherhood is voluntary.",
