    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/katha_pollitt_784259",
        "quote": "The notion that female initiative is useless because men know what they want is particularly odd - most people don't even know what they want for dinner.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Katha Pollitt",
            "url": "/quotes/katha_pollitt_784259"
