    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/katha_pollitt_784268",
        "quote": "It's a rare pro-lifer who is against the death penalty, who's against all war, who favors, you know, all the things people need to flourish and stay healthy in life. They've tied themselves to the Republican Party, which doesn't support any of that.",
